      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Delft University of Technology</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg/330px-TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg/500px-TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg/960px-TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TU_Delft_Mekelpark.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Entrance to the Mekelpark, with the statue of Prometheus, university's symbol <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Delft University of Technology</b>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delft\">Delft</a>,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Netherlands\">The Netherlands</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs_and_Authors\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs and Authors</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\">